Ex-Texas Rangers President Schieffer Is Hired by Selig to Run L.A. Dodgers

-- B y   R o b   G l o s t e r
-- 
2011-04-25T19:27:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-25/ex-texas-rangers-president-schieffer-is-hired-by-selig-to-run-l-a-dodgers.html
Major League Baseball  appointed
former Texas Rangers President J. Thomas Schieffer to run the
 Los Angeles Dodgers , according to a statement.  MLB took over operations of the club last week as
Commissioner Bud Selig said he had “deep concerns” over the
management of the franchise.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Rob Gloster in San Francisco at 
 rgloster@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Michael Sillup at 
